data.description: Character and charm! The beautiful hardwood floors and trim, original pocket doors, built-in buffet & cabinet and high ceilings warm this 4 bed, 2 bath home. Appreciate the bright, updated bathroom, spacious rooms, walk-in closets, and upper level 3/4 bath. Brand new Eco Sky High Performance Windows throughout the home installed by Mad City. They insulate like walls! Ask for more info. Tons of space in the cabinets & pantry for all your kitchen appliances and gadgets, exposed brick, stainless steel appliances, kitchen windows and slide-out shelves in the cupboard & pantry shelves in the adorable kitchen. Relax on the front porch or play yard games in your fully fenced backyard. Great location with easy access to local shopping 6 dining!
